<div class="content" name="GetDevCaps_Phone" uuid="81bf0e0b-3fb9-41fb-9c20-6fb8b9e34664"><p>The GetDevCaps packet is transmitted from a TAPI <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_60e0e1fa-66fe-41e1-b5e3-ceab97e53506" data-linktype="relative-path">client</a> to a TAPI <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_434b0234-e970-4e8c-bdfa-e16a30d96703" data-linktype="relative-path">server</a> in a <a href="489de77f-16d8-4c4f-939a-f795e8b42893#gt_8a7f6700-8311-45bc-af10-82e10accd331" data-linktype="relative-path">remote procedure call</a>.
Sending this packet queries a specified phone device to determine its telephony
capabilities.</p><table>
